  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.2.0-alpha03\" data-text=\"Version 1.2.0-alpha03\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.2.0-alpha03</h3>\n<p>September 7, 2022</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.benchmark:benchmark-*:1.2.0-alpha03</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/dd1e45e8550560087f6447a34a9145048b5766f4..cce7b70f6a5ebf955cf748a73c18b63228b22c74/benchmark\">Version 1.2.0-alpha03 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>New Features</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added experimental APIs for using <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">BenchmarkState</code> independently, separate from <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">BenchmarkRule</code> / <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">JUnit4</code>. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/Id478f193ede7bfe746439471da6b6ca46651a9dd\">Id478f</a>, <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/228489614\">b/228489614</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Leanback fallback for <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">startActivityAndWait</code>. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/01ed77e9aeafebf441ab9c4f1119f672796a72d2\">01ed77</a>, <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/242899915\">b/242899915</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
